{
  "stem": "58.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I knew he picks on young men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He wanted to show, probably, that he's stronger than we were, I was-- we were all strong but-- one day I said-- In the meantime, Hakiva Leifer got himself a job cleaning the-- they call it [GERMAN] in German.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Working in the barrack, giving out the food, cutting the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I say, Hakiva, you have to take me out of this kommando--you have to take me into work something, because it could be any day now, or any hour, if I go.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I say, you know something, give away the bread, I'll give you more soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Give away the bread to somebody else and change to go on this kommando.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I talked to some guys, and one accepted it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'll give him my bread, daily bread, and he'll take this kommando, and I'll take his-- I'll go to another group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he went for me, and I took another group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was my group?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They try to break in shoes for the front line, for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "New shoes, no socks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Their feet were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And besides this, if you were tall, they hit you over the had with a stick, That the-- that could kill you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you walked the whole day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Could imagine walking around a whole day?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day I say no, they're not going to kill me this way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got out of the line, and I went--I hid in the barrack a whole day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When the group, they came to go in to eat, to the barracks, I came out.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
